Title: Relates to prohibiting overnight parking by vehicles not registered in this state in the city of New York
Summary: Prohibits overnight parking by vehicles not registered in this state in the city of New York; permits certain guest exemptions and permits parking by persons who maintain a dwelling in NYC.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to overnight parking
